  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 0
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Thanks to PuffoThePufferfish and Blueray901165 for helping shape this game. They were the closest with it through the entire process, helping me test and improve it every step of the way.\r\n\r\nThanks to Scoops, a member of the community, for her perfect recreation of the game's stylization shader which allowed me to add performant grass and other features.\r\n\r\nThanks to Taaamas (@taaamas.bsky.social) for their pixel art of the game's desktop icon which they generously allowed me to use!\r\n\r\nThanks to the patrons who generously supported me throughout this game's long and sometimes-rocky development:\r\n\r\nWhiplasher15\r\nJeb_CC\r\nhuman forklift\r\nDial\r\nCheesyFeline\r\nFunkyPenguin\r\nPotato\r\nGIZA\r\nlololololololol\r\nSin\r\nEthan Dorais\r\nKasprong39\r\nTripleAFrog\r\nYielding\r\nStewie\r\nSpindi\r\nMeasured Moth\r\nMarchie\r\nFalcon05\r\nMoongladeCat\r\nHI-IM-ABE\r\nEcoEnemy\r\nmonk16\r\nItHamBoi\r\nOwen Dahl\r\nKalai Kamalu\r\nError.__63\r\nNuclearDiamond019%T#\r\nCezorian\r\nFuzibug\r\nTaylor Thomas\r\nAlsnapz\r\nSomething Super\r\nNimportnawak\r\nSkyjot\r\nSteel Rider\r\nvolumetric shit compressor\r\nJack Phillips\r\nLimeon\r\nJackieWorm\r\nDifferentialDial\r\nCheemMan\r\nGlassMan\r\nTheAngel\r\nThis_is_ Benji\r\nCEO of chiCKEN\r\nPatty\r\nFinsir\r\nOcarina\r\nLeah Lycorea\r\n\r\nThanks to Zenonclaw for modelling the shovel and the old elevator, which was scrapped long ago but still used for its parts.\r\n\r\nThanks to ZedFox for one of the boombox tracks (the good one) and the disco ball music.\r\n\r\nThanks to youreashotgun for the snare flea TV channel.\r\n\r\nAnd thanks to Noah, Seth, Null, Sam, Zenonclaw, ZedFox, and Joseph for helping playtest throughout early development.\r\n\r\n\r\nThanks to psyberartist for \"copperplate\" licensed under CC BY 2.0 Deed:\r\nhttps://www.flickr.com/photos/psyberartist/2370774340/in/photolist-5wLrf8-5aBQF1-4BuQBE-63DLjk-67Kygy-4ZBLXu\r\n\r\n\"Texture - Plastic\" by bzemer on DeviantArt:\r\nhttps://www.deviantart.com/bzemer/art/Texture-Plastic-260931335\r\n\r\n\"Intertwined roots of two birches next to Myrstigen hiking trail in Brastad.jpg\" by W.carter\r\nhttps://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Intertwined_roots_of_two_birches_next_to_Myrstigen_hiking_trail_in_Brastad.jpg\r\n\r\n\"Digitaria eriantha plant base1 NWS - Flickr - Macleay Grass Man.jpg\" by Harry Rose\r\nhttps://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Digitaria_eriantha_plant_base1_NWS_-_Flickr_-_Macleay_Grass_Man.jpg\r\n\r\n\"Star Anise Series (4298498430).jpg\" by THOR\r\nhttps://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Star_Anise_Series_(4298498430).jpg\r\n\r\n\"Veins Pack 1.1\" by PaldimoMedia\r\nhttps://www.deviantart.com/paldimomedia/art/Veins-Pack-1-1-49373242\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nSound effects from Freesound.org, licensed under CC-BY (Attribution). Thank you:\r\n\r\n\"Cat screaming #13.mp3\" by AUDACITIER\nhttps://freesound.org/people/AUDACITIER/sounds/634660/\n\n\"Ferry\" by Metzik\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Metzik/sounds/376404/\r\n\r\n\"peugot 206 car interior accelerating...\" by jorickhoofd\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/jorickhoofd/sounds/176641/\r\n\r\n\"Scifi_metal_door_opening_and_closing_sound\" by Artninja\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Artninja/sounds/742321/\r\n\r\n\"Wooden Door Metal Handle Slam.wav\" by Evil-Dog\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Evil-Dog/sounds/265340/\r\n\r\n\"Closing Glass Door\" by Kraftaggregat\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Kraftaggregat/sounds/736558/\r\n\r\n\"Clothing Rustle Cotton\" by leonelmail\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/leonelmail/sounds/427866/\r\n\r\n\"Monster Stomp Footsteps Sequence\" by Vilkas_Sound\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Vilkas_Sound/sounds/753178/\r\n\r\n\"Tearing Flesh\" by dereklieu\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/dereklieu/sounds/241822/\r\n\r\n\"Flowing Sand\" by SteveMeli\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/SteveMeli/sounds/215006/\r\n\r\n\"Enemy Death (Gaseous) #1\" by SilverIllusionist\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/SilverIllusionist/sounds/833358/\r\n\r\n\"Breaking Glass 1.MP3\" by FunWithSound\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/FunWithSound/sounds/390703/\r\n\r\n\"Elevator music\" by MichaeLydian\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/MichaeLydian/sounds/743697/\r\n\r\n\"Éléments Auditifs - Aube Électronique - Kjartan Abel\" by kjartan_abel\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/kjartan_abel/sounds/710950/\r\n\r\n\"hot water gushing out of a metal tap.aif\" by Tomlija\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Tomlija/sounds/110103/\r\n\r\n\"catfight2.mp3\"\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/bebops/sounds/23721/\r\n\r\n\"Canyonwind.wav\" by Burning_Cicada_Ltd\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Burning_Cicada_Ltd./sounds/496320/\r\n\r\n\"Jungle - Vietnam.m4a\" by Imartins\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/lmartins/sounds/544001/\r\n\r\n\"Drip41.wav\" by syrinscape\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/syrinscape/sounds/207615/\r\n\r\n\"Slime Squish.wav\" by Wihan98\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Wihan98/sounds/544151/\r\n\r\n\"Wet Splat\" by JustInvoke\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/JustInvoke/sounds/446115/\r\n\r\n\"Alien is crawling-002.wav\" by tosha73\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/tosha73/sounds/512952/\r\n\r\n\"Bottles Multiple Clinking\" by AshFox\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/AshFox/sounds/174863/\r\n\r\n\"Steps-Dirt-Falling_1a.Ogg\" by nuFF3\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/nuFF3/sounds/477393/\r\n\r\n\"superhero_earth_impact_hit_07062025\" by Artninja\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Artninja/sounds/815336/\r\n\r\n\"Moving-hangers-with-clothes-on-them-in-wardrobe.wav\" by sound_ims\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/sound_ims/sounds/131214/\r\n\r\n\"FX - 3 Apocalypse Trumpets\" by bolkmar\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/bolkmar/sounds/515051/\r\n\r\n\"Incoming Artillery Strike Cinematic Explosion\" by EFlexMusic\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/EFlexMusic/sounds/530886/\r\n\r\n\"Explosion.wav\" by Anrichcvs\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Anrichcvs/sounds/595888/\r\n\r\n\"mortar grenade shell 002.wav\" by klankbeeld\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/klankbeeld/sounds/344686/\r\n\r\n\"BadBreaks_Crunch_and_Snap.wav\" by sonictechtonic\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/sonictechtonic/sounds/242217/\r\n\r\n\"DenseCrunchRe-rated_CaveIn.wav\" by zimbot\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/zimbot/sounds/244484/\r\n\r\n\"panic_sound.wav\" by Davosko\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Davosko/sounds/696068/\r\n\r\n\"plastic_small_tools_drop.aiff\" by nothayama\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/nothayama/sounds/172502/\r\n\r\n\"Chiming and Alarm Beeps\" by deleted_user_5614036\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/deleted_user_5614036/sounds/369250/\r\n\r\n\"fall to ground.aif\" by MAJ061785\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/MAJ061785/sounds/85546/\r\n\r\n\"wild animal screams\" by modnara\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/modnara/sounds/459846/\r\n\r\n\"helmet_grabbing_and_handling_sound\" by Artninja\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Artninja/sounds/725314/\r\n\r\n\"Forest_Fire_Inferno.aif\" by Dynamicell\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Dynamicell/sounds/17548/\r\n\r\n\"Wooden Doors Opening and Closing\" by SonicRealityFX\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/SonicRealityFX/sounds/436869/\r\n\r\n\"Door.wav\" by campl\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/campl/sounds/138469/\r\n\r\n\"Shaking A Table\" by alirabiei\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/alirabiei/sounds/491852/\r\n\r\n\"Goldon Grand Piano - F Major - Morphagene Reel (toy piano)\" by --wash\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/--wash/sounds/490320/\r\n\r\n\"footsteps_dress_shoes_01.aif\" by tim-kahn\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/tim.kahn/sounds/44666/\r\n\r\n\"VEHSirn_Police Car Siren.Go Under SFX_EM.wav\" by newlocknew\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/newlocknew/sounds/692523/\r\n\r\n\"Shotgun Shoot and Reload.wav\" by PieTheAnimator45\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/PieTheAnimator45/sounds/608946/\r\n\r\n\"Duvet - single ruffle - 221098_AshtiHari_SD100_Term4.wav\" by 221098HariPotter\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/221098HariPotter/sounds/655594/\r\n\r\n\"Toy Double Barrel Shotgun Reloading\" by JumboSizedFish\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/JumboSizedFish/sounds/693507/\r\n\r\n\"Screaming and flying away geese, early morning at a pond, shocking\" by AtoMediaDesign\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/AtoMediaDesign/sounds/649025/\r\n\r\n\"pull cord.wav\" by andrewgnau2\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/andrewgnau2/sounds/71537/\r\n\r\n\"Dinosaur.wav\" by jamesrodavidson\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/jamesrodavidson/sounds/192364/\r\n\r\n\"Oxygenated Breathing Inside Space Helmet.wav\" by Bliss\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Bliss/sounds/167212/\r\n\r\n\"Outer Space Pad 120bpm.wav\" by mkoenig\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/mkoenig/sounds/43535/\r\n\r\n\"outer space air.wav\" by celestino.anthony\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/celestino.anthony/sounds/172457/\r\n\r\n\"Slime Creature Movement (large and messy)\" by SilverIllusionist\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/SilverIllusionist/sounds/671112/\r\n\r\n\"wobble_02.wav\" by matucha\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/matucha/sounds/116035/\r\n\r\n\"Flying Bug\" by Abacagi\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Abacagi/sounds/512363/\r\n\r\n\"Error_04.wav\" by distillerystudio\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/distillerystudio/sounds/327735/\r\n\r\n\"Metal Drop bar resonance\" by jorickhoofd\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/jorickhoofd/sounds/160086/\r\n\r\n\"Sledgehammer - using to break a block of concrete\" by SoundsnapFX\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/SoundsnapFX/sounds/583964/\r\n\r\n\"FX - walkie talkie ininteligible.wav\" by vinjatovix\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/vinjatovix/sounds/109647/\r\n\r\n\"Squelch.wav\" by Fringer_Cat\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Fringer_Cat/sounds/426083/\r\n\r\n\"26-WalkieTalkie.wav\" by Leoctiurs\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/Leoctiurs/sounds/428183/\r\n\r\n\"Eating Flesh (Loop)\" by julius_galla\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/julius_galla/sounds/322296/\r\n\r\n\"slam0.mp3\" by themfish\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/themfish/sounds/33845/\r\n\r\n\"scream-2.wav\" by _def \r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/_def/sounds/346549/\r\n\r\n\"IndustrialNoiseRhitmic 140106_02.wav\" by klankbeeld\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/klankbeeld/sounds/213228/\r\n\r\n\"Distant Steel Door Open Close Shut Creak Ambience\" by wertstahl\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/wertstahl/sounds/427608/\r\n\r\n\"FX_Vent_Foley.wav\" by PeteBarry\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/PeteBarry/sounds/474014/\r\n\r\n\"Electric_Pylon_Power Line-Buzz 01.wav\" by omnisounddesign\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/omnisounddesign/sounds/338074/\r\n\r\n\"Globo caida.wav\" by CraterZounds\r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/CraterZounds/sounds/189734/\r\n\r\n\"Skin rub (5)\" by chemicalcrux \r\nhttps://freesound.org/people/chemicalcrux/sounds/531008/\r\n\r\nThanks to TheStockWarehouse for \"Pink Flower V3\" https://www.deviantart.com/thestockwarehouse/art/Pink-Flower-V3-473444112\r\n"
